data.description: Eden, NC. Small rural town with walking trails and river access points for the Dan and Smith rivers. Convenient travel to Danville/Martinsville, VA and the Greensboro Piedmont Triad via Hwy 220/I-73 and Hwy 29. Moving to the area for work? Thinking about retiring to beautiful North Carolina? Need a larger house with extra yard space for recreation, pool or garden? LOOK NO FURTHER! This charming 4 bedroom/2 bath, older home with circular driveway is just waiting for your paintbrush and design ideas - because everything else is done! See complete list of updates including:  roof, windows, water/sewer lines, flooring, screened porch - not to mention the BEAUTIFUL original hardwood floors in many rooms. Screened porch screams Southern Hospitality!  BUYERS - call your agent today to schedule your private tour and make this gem your next home for 2024!
